Package: climniche
Type: Package
Title: Niche Relative Climate Exposure
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bohao", "He", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "bohao.he@polimi.it")
    )
Description: Decomposes projected climate change relative to the current
    realised climatic niche of a species. Using occurrence records, range data,
    binary or continuous species distribution model suitability maps, current
    environmental rasters and future projections, the package reports related
    quantities for displacement magnitude, radial niche shift, non-radial
    displacement and empirical niche boundary exceedance.
